    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为现存于世的最后一位女巫，紫罗兰却连在生死攸关之时施展法术都做不到。紫罗兰的一次意外，打破了宇宙的魔法平衡，自身蕴藏的魔力得以释放，代价则是灵界之神的力量被她通通窃取。猫头鹰神不得已被迫协助紫罗兰。同他们一道收拾这烂摊——或者说是这场冒失的“苦旅”……旅途中也对抗那些与你有着相同目标的异端审判者和其他不速之客。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385490/extras/52930b82127f8de9a078a619c3362692.poster.avif?t=1756663465\" width=472 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385490/extras/52930b82127f8de9a078a619c3362692.webm?t=1756663465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385490/extras/52930b82127f8de9a078a619c3362692.mp4?t=1756663465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>    </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握并精通施法技艺：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由绘制各式各样的符文，没有任何时间或区域限制，即时绘制符文以释放法术，真正的魔法师就该这样无拘无束！使用你的鼠标、控制器、触摸屏或绘图板作为魔杖来绘制符文，无需担心会成为猎物行动的目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385490/extras/03822b9096768b2bd43be76ac4abbf23.poster.avif?t=1756663465\" width=454 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385490/extras/03822b9096768b2bd43be76ac4abbf23.webm?t=1756663465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385490/extras/03822b9096768b2bd43be76ac4abbf23.mp4?t=1756663465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >想想真正的巫师会怎么做：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发挥创造力，融合各类法术，让不同的法术组合碰撞出别样的火花！发挥想象力，用收集到的草药制作出不同效果的护身符与魔药。发挥聪明才智，制定打败敌人的有效策略，跳上扫帚，恢复宇宙的魔法平衡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385490/extras/9ff912eeb738b53f24335f1fcf7ebbeb.poster.avif?t=1756663465\" width=456 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385490/extras/9ff912eeb738b53f24335f1fcf7ebbeb.webm?t=1756663465\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2385490/extras/9ff912eeb738b53f24335f1fcf7ebbeb.mp4?t=1756663465\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
